high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the bed, turn left at the bed, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the shelves.
Take the watch from the shelf.
Move to the right while facing the shelves.
Put the watch in the white bowl on the upper shelf.
Take the bowl from the shelves.
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the space between the beds, go forward to the night stand.
Put the bowl on the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a watch in it on a night stand.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward toward the bed, turn left, go forward, turn right at the end of the bed, then go straight to the shelves.
Pick up the watch from the left most shelf.
Move to the right, and look up to the shelf with the bowl on it.
Place the watch in the bowl on the shelf.
Pick up the bowl with the watch in it from the shelf.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to go between the beds.
Put the bowl on the night stand, between the beds.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a watch in it on the nightstand.

high_descs: Move to the shelf at the foot of the bed
Pick up a watch from the shelf
Move to the right side of the shelf
Put the watch in a bowl
Pick up the bowl from the shelf
Move to the end table in between the two beds
Put the bowl on the end table
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a watch on the end table in between the two beds.
